  "body": "<img alt=\"3a-IMG_1018.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834344735-1173G500LPM2ENJXI5X0/3a-IMG_1018.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3b-unnamed-4.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834344421-UD89GVU3PYN71TODRX1C/3b-unnamed-4.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3c-IMG_1070.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834345307-M1HQ7YXSMFQIR4CHBMKU/3c-IMG_1070.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3d-IMG_1075.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834345848-IW67IHJKBLY5R5I8WRUM/3d-IMG_1075.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3e-IMG_1061.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834346331-KM4V2GNV1R6YDHZR8YF6/3e-IMG_1061.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3f-IMG_1080.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834348907-D8VLL7DKD2FOBC5ZNACU/3f-IMG_1080.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3g-unnamed-1.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834348545-E1LQY4001K8FFEV52AAO/3g-unnamed-1.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3h-unnamed.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834350712-IT930YFLLRMVW2H0ETQ6/3h-unnamed.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3i-IMG_1073.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834350423-BXAAE2ALA6VR64L52403/3i-IMG_1073.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3j-IMG_0986.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834352107-O4IS0SZB3Y47ZFOYNTXS/3j-IMG_0986.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3k-IMG_1064.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834352161-WYJSVG8LG0MAK8ESQO7Y/3k-IMG_1064.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3l-IMG_1085.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834353189-P40YF3CMG0XA70V9LVF7/3l-IMG_1085.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3m-IMG_1081.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834352959-PS1KJFJR1GMZNXOPXZJ2/3m-IMG_1081.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3n-unnamed-3.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834354318-4LO59L8ZGFORZZTXCXYV/3n-unnamed-3.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3o-unnamed-2.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595834354793-RLSBO74PQ0ZAB8MK8DCI/3o-unnamed-2.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>So many awesome moments from Creativation. As much fun as it is seeing brand new products, it's the connecting with people that tops it all off. Perhaps that's why I couldn't make <a href=\"https://youtu.be/i48L7xmVauU\">the video</a> any shorter, but I hope you enjoy it and feel like you were right there with us!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>On A Whim is now in stores - please check with your local retailer or shop online at <a href=\"http://bit.ly/onawhim\">Simon Says Stamp </a>and <a href=\"http://bit.ly/onawhim1\">Scrapbook.com</a>!  PS - We will be announcing our Design Team on Friday! Thanks so much for your patience!</p>"
